Package ie.gmit.dip

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IConsoleInput
    Interface for reading input from a console.
    IConsoleOutput
    Interface for writing to a console.
    IGui
    Interface abstracting a user interface that can read from a user and write back to them.
    IMapper
    Interface for mapping common words to their synonyms.
    IParser
    Interface for a string parser.
    ISwapper
    Interface for swapping synonyms with common words.
    ITextFile
    Interface for accessing text files.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ConsoleInput
    Reads user input from the System in stream.
    ConsoleOutput
    Writes back to a user via the standard console.
    Gui
    User interface that uses console input and output to communicate with the user.
    Mapper
    A mapper that maps synonyms to common words using a hashmap.
    Parser
    A parser that breaks an String input into tokens by using a delimiter.
    Runner
    Runner of the application.
    Swapper
    A swapper that uses an IParser and IMapper to swap input strings and produce outputs.
    TextFile
    A text file representation where the contents of the file come from an existing file in the file system.
    TextFileMock
    A virtual text file where the contents are injected as a list of lines.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    EConsoleColour
    Styling colors for console.
